es.stuker.buker.ipv6multidest.webserver

Class Scanner

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.stuker.buker.ipv6multidest.webserver.Scanner

  • class Scanner
extends java.lang.Object
    Webserver log scanner. Log parser class. Contains multiple regexp to match structures of the log entries. Generates request object for every line or log entry.
    Author:
    Jorge D'iez de la Fuente
